      <p>
        Velvet Assassin is inspired by the fascinating story and unbreakable spirit of British
        secret agent Violette Szabo. Take control of Violette Summer, a beautiful World War II
        spy deep behind enemy lines with no support or official backing from the British Government.
         Intense stealth action with a startling real-time lighting system and surreal visuals combine
         to produce an incredible gaming experience.
       </p>
       <p>
Through third-person game play, sneak up on enemies and pull the pins from their belted grenades.
 Infiltrate a Gestapo prison and slip cyanide to your own men before the Germans make them talk.
 Slink through the shadows to finish off your unsuspecting enemies with a single, silent move.
 Through Violette's fever dreams, experience what she experienced. Walk where she walked ... and kill those she killed.
